now this is a physical journal account of the journey, but I would have edited some of the book. I did enjoy the poetry that was interspersed throughout the journal. Very moving. \u003cbr /\u003eAll in all, this is a good book for someone to read to help you understand the toll that a serious illness takes on the patient and those that love the patient. \u003cbr /\u003e#MoreThanLoveAHusbandsTale #Peter Forster","rating":4,"shelving":{"__typename":"Shelving","shelf":{"__typename":"Shelf","name":"read","webUrl":"https://www.goodreads.com/review/list/3505196?shelf=read"},"taggings":[],"webUrl":"https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/3307111970"},"likeCount":59,"viewerHasLiked":null,"commentCount":0,"viewerCanComment({\"resourceType\":\"review\"})":null},"User:47722544":{"id":47722544,"__typename":"User","legacyId":47722544,"imageUrlSquare":"https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/users/1498516338i/47722544._UY200_CR33,0,200,200_.jpg","isAuthor":false,"textReviewsCount":1680,"viewableName":"Pegboard","isBlockedByViewer":false,"webUrl":"https://www.goodreads.com/user/show/47722544-pegboard","contributor":null,"isFollowing":false,"isFriend":false,"followersCount":9},"Review:kca://review:goodreads/amzn1.gr.review:goodreads.v1.kc3L9tyXLhuJz4FZaP9xhQ":{"id":"kca://review:goodreads/amzn1.gr.review:goodreads.v1.kc3L9tyXLhuJz4FZaP9xhQ","__typename":"Review","book":{"__ref":"Book:kca://book/amzn1.gr.book.v3.gL5m_yuvtskpQjYV"},"creator":{"__ref":"User:47722544"},"recommendFor":null,"updatedAt":1643520886640,"createdAt":1581610588069,"spoilerStatus":false,"lastRevisionAt":1581610601992,"text":"More Than Love, A Husband’s tale by Peter B Forster is an unaltered account the challenges, emotions, and regrets he experienced during the last few months of his wife’s life. There are many spouses that can relate to the helplessness Peter faced, and by reading his book it can give you a clear view of how to make the most out of a horrific situation. \u003cbr /\u003e 